## III. WHY MAGA RESONATES (AXIOM EXPLANATION)

MAGA succeeds because:

1. **It restores certainty** in an uncertain world
2. **It collapses complexity** into identity
3. **It gives moral clarity** when institutions feel hollow
4. **It provides belonging** when social cohesion erodes

> When institutions fail to supply meaning, movements do.

